<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="page-header">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Our Visionaries</h1>
                    <p>Meet the visionaries guiding Nageshwaram Foundation towards a brighter future.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 50px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 60px;">
                        <div style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                            <img src="/images/founder-placeholder.jpg" alt="Founder Image"
                                style="width: 300px; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; border: 5px solid var(--bg-cream); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); margin: 0 auto;">
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex: 2; align-self: center;">
                            <h2 style="color: var(--accent-gold);">Message from the Founder</h2>
                            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Shri Nageshwar Singh</h3>
                            <p class="founder-quote"
                                style="font-style: italic; font-size: 1.2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-gold); padding-left: 20px; color: #555;">
                                "Education is not just about literacy; it is about liberation. It is the key
                                that unlocks the golden door of freedom and opportunity. My dream is to see
                                every child in our village equipped with the knowledge and values to lead a life
                                of dignity and purpose."
                            </p>
                            <p>With decades of social service and a heart beating for the community, Shri
                                Nageshwar Singh laid the foundation of this trust to return to society the
                                blessings of knowledge.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="trustee-list text-center">
                        <h2>Board of Trustees</h2>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 40px;">Our distinguished board members bringing diverse
                            expertise to our mission.</p>
                        <div class="card-row">
                            <div class="card trustee-card">
                                <div
                                    style="width: 100px; height: 100px; background: #eee; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px;">
                                </div>
                                <h3>Trustee Name 1</h3>
                                <p style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 500;">Chairman</p>
                                <p>bringing 20+ years of educational administration experience.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card trustee-card">
                                <div
                                    style="width: 100px; height: 100px; background: #eee; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px;">
                                </div>
                                <h3>Trustee Name 2</h3>
                                <p style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 500;">Secretary</p>
                                <p>Dedicated social worker with a focus on rural development.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card trustee-card">
                                <div
                                    style="width: 100px; height: 100px; background: #eee; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px;">
                                </div>
                                <h3>Trustee Name 3</h3>
                                <p style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 500;">Treasurer</p>
                                <p>Ensuring transparency and ethical management of resources.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>